# PhishGuard — Project Review Document

> **Project:** PhishGuard — AI-Powered Phishing Detection Application
> **Date:** February 27, 2026
> **Repository Root:** `phish-guard-main/`

---

## 1. Project Overview

PhishGuard is a **full-stack web application** that detects phishing attacks in real-time. Users can paste a URL, email, SMS message, or upload a QR code / screenshot / PDF, and the app analyzes it using a combination of:
- **AI-powered Supabase Edge Functions** (server-side)
- **Client-side heuristic fallback** (offline-safe)
- **Third-party threat intelligence APIs**

