## 5. Core Logic: `src/lib/api.ts`

This is the heart of the **client-side intelligence layer** (721 lines):

| Function | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `detectPhishing()` | Calls Supabase Edge Function; falls back to local detection on error |
| `performLocalDetection()` | Full heuristic analysis (domains, keywords, lookalike, forensics) |
| `fetchDNSRecords()` | DNS-over-HTTPS via Cloudflare for A, MX, TXT records |
| `fetchDomainAge()` | OSINT via Wayback Machine CDX API to get domain first-seen date |
| `detectLookalikeAttack()` | Character substitution detection (e.g. `g00gle.com` → `google.com`) |
| `expandShortUrl()` | Resolves bit.ly/tinyurl via unshorten.me API |
| `checkSemanticContext()` | Urgency + grammar pattern analysis |
| `addToScanHistory()` | Saves to DB (authenticated) or localStorage (anonymous) |
| `migrateLocalHistoryToDb()` | Moves localStorage history to DB on sign-in |

